👋 Hi, I'm Taimoor khan. I am a skilled Webflow professional specializing in creating custom websites using Webflow, converting Figma/XD designs to Webflow, and resolving webflow problems & bugs.

My passion for design and unwavering commitment to delivering high-quality work enable me to transform your vision into a tangible online reality. By working together, we can elevate your digital presence and achieve your online goals. Please do not hesitate to contact me to discuss how we can collaborate and bring your vision to life.

description.content:
WEBFLOW | WEBFLOW WEBSITE | FIGMA TO WEBFLOW|


Greetings,


I am Taimoor khan With 4 years of experience and 400+ successful webflow projects on Fiverr, I specialize in creating high-performance, visually stunning Webflow websites. Whether it's Figma to Webflow, XD to Webflow, or Sketch to Webflow, I'll bring your design to life.


What You Will Get in This Gig:


  • Figma to webflow Conversion
  • Complete Webflow Website
  • Full Webflow Development
  • Design, Redesign, or Develop a Webflow Website
  • Responsive, User-friendly Design
  • CMS for FAQ, Blog, dynamic filtering, Finsweet Client First etc
  • Advanced Interactions and Animations
  • CMS (Content Management System) Setup
  • Fast Delivery with Top-Quality Assurance


Why Choose Me?

  •  Unlimited revisions.
  •  Quick delivery.
  •  15 days support


What I Need from You:

Provide the design files (Figma, XD, Sketch, PSD, etc.) or a reference site, and I'll bring it to Webflow.


Let's Get Started!

Feel free to message me to discuss your project details.
